text: Choi Gyong-hui (born 23 May 1973) is a North Korean gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:North Korean female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of North Korea Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Gymnasts at the 1990 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for North Korea Category:Medalists at the 1990 Asian Games
